    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>When you hit a &amp;Reference[fiend]{fiend} or an &amp;Reference[undead]{undead} with this magic weapon, that creature takes an extra 2d6 &amp;Reference[radiant]{radiant} damage. If the target has 25 hit points or fewer after taking this damage, it must succeed on a [[/save wis 15 format=long]] or be destroyed. On a successful save, the creature becomes &amp;Reference[frightened]{frightened} of you until the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>While you hold this weapon, it sheds bright light in a 20-foot radius and dim light for an additional 20 feet.</p>\n</div>",
